info.name: Oracle WebLogic Server Local File Inclusion
author: paradessia
narluin
info.description: An easily exploitable local file inclusion vulnerability allows unauthenticated attackers with network access via HTTP to compromise Oracle WebLogic Server. Supported versions that are affected are 12.1.3.0.0, 12.2.1.3.0, 12.2.1.4.0 and 14.1.1.0.0. Successful attacks of this vulnerability can result in unauthorized and sometimes complete access to critical data.
